    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and roughly chop your<strong> brown onion[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>and <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p><p>Separate your <strong>coriander leaves </strong>from their stems, then finely chop the stems (save the leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>in half</p>",
