            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the meatballs are browning, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>carrot</strong> and  <strong>pepper</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz until smooth</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1696851244106-x200.jpg",
