    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky chipotle pork meatballs</strong> over the <strong>drained spaghetti</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and <strong>coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
